             <p style="margin-left: 10px; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 13px;">@Shailja believes smiling at strangers isn't weird. What's your take?</p>
             <h4 style="margin-left: 10px; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 13px;"><%= @post.title %></h4>
          <table width="100%">
    <tr>
